野例番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189fe63e9d0b405b58a554aeca4e8647e5307477","tid":552703,"uid":45368,"like":35,"dislike":6,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:40:11.000Z","msg":"同fd去玩發覺租落既飯店浴室係用落地玻璃牆<br />\n但租左就無計唯有照住<br />\n夜晚玩完返黎大家都好攰咁<br />\n因為我好想早d訓所以咪話我沖涼先<br />\n入到浴室咪背住佢除衫沖涼<br />\n隔住玻璃睇到佢開左電視睇，但細心留睇發覺佢成日偷偷地𣈴過黎浴室<br />\n佢紅都面哂，我見佢咁可愛都忍唔住扯左<br />\n沖到一半發覺唔記得拎衫入去換咪想話叫佢幫下手<br />\n佢半遮住塊面咁怕怕醜醜咁推開隻門比衫我<br />\n我知佢見到我碌野已經硬撚哂<br />\n我一手拖左佢入浴室<br />\n同佢攬埋一舊問佢想唔想要<br />\n佢唔應我，我一野嘴落佢到同佢大車左成分鐘<br />\n再一邊除埋佢d衫褲<br />\n當除左佢條牛仔褲時發覺仲硬過我<br />\n咁之後d野唔講啦<br />\n都係個d野咁啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：非GAY"},{"pid":"fd6fb7ff07040e9d61f039394144829df1a2b5a8","tid":552703,"uid":89064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:56:14.000Z","msg":"全部hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6291ad4b91f1fa6aaf2a84873d2c8d798308f79b","tid":552703,"uid":170297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cf3f8c09c033a3afeb31f80c783010f86fdc9a94","tid":552703,"uid":152437,"like":67,"dislike":8,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:58:10.000Z","msg":"睇到扯扯地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeccc4e3e9c498ffabf890901593d0550b310e6","tid":552703,"uid":56546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"375a0e95a5ad940314acf677f4ddf96d84606815","tid":552703,"uid":59782,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"cf3f8c09c033a3afeb31f8